{"tid":1673681,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鞭反加泰集會鞭埋今晚就好，但抗爭心態上嘅問題一定要持續鞭策唔停得","createTime":"2019-10-24T19:27:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-26T11:27:11.000Z","uid":16846,"like":37,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"bb5d653fceb4b8fe1229156858fdc9322f61f3a3","tid":1673681,"uid":16846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T19:27:32.000Z","msg":"本來喺南亞仔個post打，喺度貼多次<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">單講加泰確實係bin完今晚就好，但有幾個位其實真係要一路bin，時刻提醒手足唔好跌入思考陷阱</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">首先呢幾日，反集會嗰班做曬手足間最唔應做嘅嘢</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>屈手足係鬼、唔fact check、齋屌唔做、甚至話要私了手足</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屈手足係鬼：</span></span><br />\n今次集會的確係有較爭議，但肯定有啲論點喺第日搞新疆、印尼嗰類大家都支持嘅集會時，五毛會重施故技，屈唔到呢樣就屈人嗰樣。班可疑人，一開始屈陳浩天等人背景可疑，跟住見自決、G20、本民前等開始撐，就改口話NCM Yue唔撐。當學界遊說團同gphone都話問過NCM Yue冇問題後，就再話支那口交部撐加獨。<br />\n1. <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">大家要培養自己critical thinking</span></span>，仔細諗下人哋「解讀」NCM Yue嘅說話有冇錯。人哋講明唔想做大台，如果見到有班人不停當佢嘅說話係神諭、聖旨，就要諗下佢哋係咪想捧殺令NCM Yue唔可信。好彩薑係老嘅辣，今日NCM Yue一個tweet收咗成班青山派皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。（其實有前科，之前成班休息撚吹風話NCM Yue唔撐暴力，結果證明對美國人嚟講香港人而家仲喺BB班<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n2. 支那口交部只係打口水交，唔係堅撐加獨、加州獨、蘇獨等。<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">支那撐加獨、加獨又撐我哋香港人，咁支那係咪一路屌我哋一路撐我哋呀？</span></span><br />\n3. 有班人呢幾日不停誇大今次集會嘅影響。<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">其實香港作為歐美剿共嘅利器，佢哋又點捨得因為今晚就放棄消滅支共？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔fact check：</span></span><br />\n1. 用少數極左喺舊年舉共產黨旗(唔係支那/支共旗)嘅相，屈加泰整體撐共。事實上加泰同香港一樣，示威嘅人實有唔同政治光譜㗎啦。而加泰人嘅政治光譜或多或少可以從選舉結果睇到，而極左喺當地市場極細，主要政黨都只係中間偏左/右。<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">但有班人唔FC就當執到寶咁周圍貼。</span></span><br />\n2. 用西班牙國民警衛隊做source嘅新聞，去話加泰收咗中共錢想搞中央銀行。明顯biased source嚟，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">除咗fact check新聞內容外，fact check仲要check埋嗰個傳媒同埋佢引用嘅source，本身立場同埋公信力高唔高。</span></span><br />\n3. 用流亡政府主席當年話中國唔同俄羅斯嘅新聞，攻擊加泰人整體親共。<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">但今次示威去到呢個地步，或多或少都係因為啲西班牙死黑警，搞到好多人激於義憤先上街。</span></span></span>就好似香港唔少中年人銀髮族甚至前淺藍咁。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">齋屌唔做：</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">不停喺連登問點解唔搞埋（其他地方），但自己完全冇諗住兄弟爬山。</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">但同時間已有手足申請11月2日同9日搞類似國際集會，證明要做根本唔難。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">話要私了手足：呢個真係屌你老母</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">最後加埋：加泰嗰面有人因為撐我哋俾支那人打啊！唔係咁都唔撐啊？</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">就算你真係咁冇信心，請憑住一路以嚟「每逢手足貌似做柒咗啲嘢，共匪就一定會做件柒到加零一嘅嘢蓋過我哋」嘅好運，有任何活動都好，你一開始唔撐都咪亂咁杞人憂天、搬弄啲唔存在嘅壞處出嚟叫人散水啦。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">何況而家集會已完，你竟然唔係煲大支那人喺加泰鬧事，而係繼續話搞手係鬼、繼續質疑集會有咩意思？令支那人再出醜夠意思喇啩？</span></span>"},{"pid":"0bbd94f2099964c16f88af07c90b7cc688499e8a","tid":1673681,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T19:27:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Squwor1.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSquwor1.gif&h=dc4a280e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=wRNUG5%2F8jzvhtT%2FDMFjpNn8q8VOs0%2BPBwwlvB7nX800%3D&h=8f564976\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"f4a91c22dcefc48592e5d3a868de9849a42036d9","tid":1673681,"uid":16846,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T19:28:10.000Z","msg":"答我<br />\n而家唔推支那人喺加泰鬧事<br />\n而係繼續質疑集會有咩用嗰班人<br />\n你哋係咩心態"},{"pid":"d368a803d518a3654317447c6e60ba594196be57","tid":1673681,"uid":288583,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f4a91c22dcefc48592e5d3a868de9849a42036d9","tid":1673681,"uid":16846,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T19:28:10.000Z","msg":"答我<br />\n而家唔推支那人喺加泰鬧事<br />\n而係繼續質疑集會有咩用嗰班人<br />\n你哋係咩心態"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T19:29:46.000Z","msg":"岩呀 屌都屌夠啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不完美，可接受，要改進<br />\n啲狗都識啦"},{"pid":"fba9b46660e250e1ffed2ed5d571eb44a65d117f","tid":1673681,"uid":223146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T19:31:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"14d9651307320ac13401e9b48f6a3d49a4be27ba","tid":1673681,"uid":16846,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T19:32:25.000Z","msg":"負皮撚樣，夠薑駁我呀<br />\n彭斯有冇割我哋蓆呀<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n加泰人為撐我哋而俾支那人打，我哋都WFC佢哋就叫割蓆喇</span></span>"},{"pid":"77e046950239691ce37db290842dbb6b07f1fc09","tid":1673681,"uid":104446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T19:34:14.000Z","msg":"講出心聲"},{"pid":"3d4c13e3d444996ffea98679b4eb6227ae5c40d4","tid":1673681,"uid":16846,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d368a803d518a3654317447c6e60ba594196be57","tid":1673681,"uid":288583,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f4a91c22dcefc48592e5d3a868de9849a42036d9","tid":1673681,"uid":16846,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T19:28:10.000Z","msg":"答我<br />\n而家唔推支那人喺加泰鬧事<br />\n而係繼續質疑集會有咩用嗰班人<br />\n你哋係咩心態"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T19:29:46.000Z","msg":"岩呀 屌都屌夠啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不完美，可接受，要改進<br />\n啲狗都識啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T19:35:49.000Z","msg":"難聽啲講，有01狗同三毛帶風向就梗㗎喇。睇下今晚過後仲繼續質疑嘅人都少咗就知咩事。<br />\n但仲質疑緊嗰班人，真係要用腦諗下，自己呢幾日俾風向狗灌咗幾多迷藥落肚，搞到個人冇曬批判思考、理性分析能力。然後反省返，下次行動唔好再咁容易上風向狗嘅當。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebb7c2476d8873938c0ce9191d16b96823b5dc3f","tid":1673681,"uid":150742,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T19:36:48.000Z","msg":"但在一個群體中提出某種主張，群體中必然會出現支持和反對的意見，分歧會以不同的方式呈現。同樣道理，即使同以改變社會為己任，社會運動的參與者亦會因為各事的緩急輕重而有所分歧，甚或是分裂。<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">在實現民主之前，也許我們必須先實踐民主</span></span>，理解各種分歧，珍惜彼此的差異，並以此為凝聚更大力量的契機，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">只有獨裁才容不下其他的聲音。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n梁天琦：寫在判刑前 (2018)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1057614\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1057614&d=wRNUG5%2F8jzvhtT%2FDMFjpNn8q8VOs0%2BPBwwlvB7nX800%3D&h=1adda88c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1057614&h=0dca4d2e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1057614</a>"},{"pid":"b7240ce55ca2fc99bc06805d923384b5fa16cb02","tid":1673681,"uid":16846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ebb7c2476d8873938c0ce9191d16b96823b5dc3f","tid":1673681,"uid":150742,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T19:36:48.000Z","msg":"但在一個群體中提出某種主張，群體中必然會出現支持和反對的意見，分歧會以不同的方式呈現。同樣道理，即使同以改變社會為己任，社會運動的參與者亦會因為各事的緩急輕重而有所分歧，甚或是分裂。<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">在實現民主之前，也許我們必須先實踐民主</span></span>，理解各種分歧，珍惜彼此的差異，並以此為凝聚更大力量的契機，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">只有獨裁才容不下其他的聲音。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n梁天琦：寫在判刑前 (2018)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1057614\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1057614&d=wRNUG5%2F8jzvhtT%2FDMFjpNn8q8VOs0%2BPBwwlvB7nX800%3D&h=1adda88c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1057614&h=0dca4d2e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1057614</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T19:40:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">話過要私了集會搞手嗰班人<br />\n如果你唔係三毛而只係被帶風向嘅<br />\n要反省下自己其實係咪真係想要民主</span></span>"},{"pid":"23838c0524cc9725ec49aee54f5e8cc472a925df","tid":1673681,"uid":142916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T19:51:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b8b7da8c6eee12274b058f5177f9e532c85be56d","tid":1673681,"uid":16846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T20:06:36.000Z","msg":"答我<br />\n而家唔推支那人喺加泰鬧事<br />\n而係繼續質疑集會有咩用嗰班人<br />\n你哋係咩心態"},{"pid":"ba70c1f1b03d6b2b2b3c26b6801aa7bd8c897f00","tid":1673681,"uid":50873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T20:17:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"587ee88a7ff342889846a45381d91f63ffd30df7","tid":1673681,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T20:24:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eeRe8aS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeeRe8aS.png&h=29d76928&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n睇到呢條撚樣講既野就知點解前幾日CC台群魔亂舞咁"},{"pid":"7e6084efa9494f255018af6b332a232ec6e01f97","tid":1673681,"uid":16846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"587ee88a7ff342889846a45381d91f63ffd30df7","tid":1673681,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score